    "#is mentioned during war time\n",
    "sid = SentimentIntensityAnalyzer()\n",
    "p=0\n",
    "n=0\n",
    "\n",
    "\n",
    "for sentence in text6:\n",
    "       \n",
    "        ss = sid.polarity_scores(sentence)\n",
    "        for k in ss:\n",
    "            if ss['compound'] >= 0.05 :\n",
    "                p=p+1\n",
    "            if ss['compound']<=0.05:\n",
    "                n=n+1\n",
    "            \n",
    "           \n",
    " \n",
    "  \n",

    "\n",

    "#Using the sentiment analyser to gauge the number of positive and negative contexts when 'war' \n",
    "#is mentioned during peace time\n",
    "sid = SentimentIntensityAnalyzer()\n",
    "p1=0\n",
    "n1=0\n",
    "\n",
    "for sentence in text92:\n",
    "       \n",
    "        ss = sid.polarity_scores(sentence)\n",
    "        for k in ss:\n",
    "            if ss['compound'] >= 0.05 :\n",
    "                p1=p1+1\n",
    "            if ss['compound']<=0.05:\n",
    "                n1=n1+1\n",
    "            \n",
    " \n",
    "  \n",
    "print(\"During peace times, the context of 'war':\\n\")\n",
    "\n",
    "print(\"Overall positive sentences:\")\n",
    "print(p1,'\\n')\n",
    "\n",
    "print(\"Overall negative sentences\")\n",
    "print(n1)\n",
    "\n",
    "    \n"
   ]
